trans-unit.source: Specifies settings that apply to a single, printed page.
trans-unit.target: Angir innstillinger som gjelder for en enkelt, trykt side.

trans-unit.source: The PageSettings class is used to specify settings that modify the way a page will be printed.
trans-unit.target: Klassen PageSettings brukes til å angi innstillinger som endrer måten en skrives.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you set default settings for all pages to be printed through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.DefaultPageSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis angir du standardinnstillingene for alle sider skrives via den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.DefaultPageSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.DefaultPageSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To specify settings on a page-by-page basis, handle the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.QueryPageSettings?displayProperty=fullName> event and modify the PageSettings argument included in the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs> or <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.QueryPageSettingsEventArgs>, respectively.
trans-unit.target: For å angi innstillinger for side ved side, kan du behandle den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.QueryPageSettings?displayProperty=fullName>hendelsen og endre PageSettings argumentet som er inkludert i den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs>eller <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.QueryPageSettingsEventArgs>henholdsvis.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.QueryPageSettingsEventArgs> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.QueryPageSettings?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information about handling <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> events, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> class overview.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om behandling <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>hendelser, kan du se den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>klassen oversikt.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>

trans-unit.source: For more information about printing, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om utskrift av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>Oversikt over navneområde.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"></xref> class using the default printer.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"> </xref> klasse bruker standardskriver.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes all fields to their default values.
trans-unit.target: Standardkonstruktøren initialiserer alle felt til standardverdiene.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you do not create an instance of <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>, but instead use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.DefaultPageSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to set settings for all pages.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis, oppretter du ikke en forekomst av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>, men i stedet bruke den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.DefaultPageSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å angi innstillinger for alle sider.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.DefaultPageSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"></xref> class using a specified printer.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av en angitt skriver.

trans-unit.source: The PageSettings constructor is similar to initializing a new instance of <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings> and setting the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterSettings%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren PageSettings ligner initialisering av en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>og innstilling av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterSettings%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterSettings%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings"></xref> that describes the printer to use.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings"> </xref> som beskriver skriveren som skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: Gets the size of the page, taking into account the page orientation specified by the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Landscape*> property.
trans-unit.target: Henter størrelsen på siden tar hensyn retningen på angitt av den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Landscape*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Landscape*>

trans-unit.source: Use the Bounds property along with the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Margins%2A> property to calculate the printing area for the page.
trans-unit.target: Bruke egenskapen grensene sammen med den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Margins%2A>til å beregne utskrift området for siden.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Margins%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"></xref> that represents the length and width, in hundredths of an inch, of the page.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"> </xref> som representerer lengde og bredde hundredeler tomme, på siden.

trans-unit.source: The printer named in the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property does not exist.
trans-unit.target: Skriveren navnet i den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen finnes ikke.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of this <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en kopi av denne <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A copy of this object.
trans-unit.target: En kopi av dette objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the page should be printed in color.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om siden skal skrives i farger.

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.SupportsColor%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to determine if the printer supports color printing.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.SupportsColor%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å fastslå om skriveren støtte for utskrift.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.SupportsColor%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If the printer supports color, but you do not want to print in color, set the Color property to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis skriveren støtter farge, men du ikke vil skrive ut i farger, angi farge egenskapen `false`.

trans-unit.source: The default will be `true`.
trans-unit.target: Standard blir `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the page should be printed in color; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis siden skal skrives i farger. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is determined by the printer.
trans-unit.target: Standard bestemmes av skriveren.

trans-unit.source: The printer named in the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property does not exist.
trans-unit.target: Skriveren navnet i den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen finnes ikke.

trans-unit.source: Copies the relevant information from the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"></xref> to the specified <xref uid="langword_csharp_DEVMODE " name="DEVMODE " href=""></xref>structure.
trans-unit.target: Overfører relevant informasjon fra den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"> </xref> til den angitte <xref uid="langword_csharp_DEVMODE " name="DEVMODE " href=""> </xref>struktur.

trans-unit.source: Call the CopyToHdevmode method to copy relevant information to a `DEVMODE` structure from a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>.
trans-unit.target: Kall metoden CopyToHdevmode for å kopiere relevant informasjon til en `DEVMODE` strukturen fra <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>

trans-unit.source: This method is useful when you want to make unmanaged Win32 calls that require a `DEVMODE`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er nyttig når du vil gjøre ubehandlet Win32-kall som krever en `DEVMODE`.

trans-unit.source: To copy information from a `DEVMODE` structure to the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>, call <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.SetHdevmode%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Slik kopierer du informasjon fra en `DEVMODE` strukturen til <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>kan du kontakte <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.SetHdevmode%2A>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.SetHdevmode%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>

trans-unit.source: The handle to a Win32 <xref uid="langword_csharp_DEVMODE" name="DEVMODE" href=""></xref> structure.
trans-unit.target: Referanse til en Win32 <xref uid="langword_csharp_DEVMODE" name="DEVMODE" href=""> </xref> struktur.

trans-unit.target: Skriveren navnet i den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen finnes ikke eller det er ingen standardskriver er installert.

trans-unit.source: Gets the x-coordinate, in hundredths of an inch, of the hard margin at the left of the page.
trans-unit.target: Henter x-koordinaten, hundredeler tomme, på harddisken margen til venstre på siden.

trans-unit.source: The hard margin represents the physical margin set by the printer.
trans-unit.target: Harddisken margen representerer fysisk margen angitt av skriveren.

trans-unit.source: The x-coordinate, in hundredths of an inch, of the left-hand hard margin.
trans-unit.target: X-koordinaten, hundredeler tomme, på venstre harddisken margen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the y-coordinate, in hundredths of an inch, of the hard margin at the top of the page.
trans-unit.target: Henter y-koordinaten, hundredeler tomme, på harddisken margen på toppen av siden.

trans-unit.source: The hard margin represents the physical margin set by the printer.
trans-unit.target: Harddisken margen representerer fysisk margen angitt av skriveren.

trans-unit.source: The y-coordinate, in hundredths of an inch, of the hard margin at the top of the page.
trans-unit.target: Y-koordinaten, hundredeler tomme, på harddisken margen på toppen av siden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the page is printed in landscape or portrait orientation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om siden skrives ut i liggende eller stående retning.

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.LandscapeAngle%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to determine the angle, in degrees, that the portrait orientation is rotated to produce the landscape orientation.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.LandscapeAngle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å fastslå vinkel i grader, at stående roteres for å produsere liggende.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.LandscapeAngle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the page should be printed in landscape orientation; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis siden skal skrives liggende; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is determined by the printer.
trans-unit.target: Standard bestemmes av skriveren.

trans-unit.target: Skriveren navnet i den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen finnes ikke.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the margins for this page.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir marger for denne siden.

trans-unit.source: When handling the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName> event, you can use this property along with the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Bounds%2A> property to calculate the printing area for the page.
trans-unit.target: Under behandling av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>hendelse, kan du bruke denne egenskapen sammen med den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Bounds%2A>til å beregne utskrift området for siden.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Bounds%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.Margins"></xref> that represents the margins, in hundredths of an inch, for the page.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.Margins"> </xref> som representerer margene hundredeler tomme, for siden.

trans-unit.source: The default is 1-inch margins on all sides.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 1-tomme marger på alle sider.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the paper size for the page.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir størrelsen på arket for siden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize> represents the size of the paper through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize.Kind%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, which contains one of the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperKind> values.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize>representerer størrelsen på arket via den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize.Kind%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen som inneholder ett av de <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperKind>verdier.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize.Kind%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize>

trans-unit.source: Set the PaperSize property for the page to a valid <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize>, available through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSizes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen PaperSize for side til en gyldig <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize>, tilgjengelig via den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSizes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlingen.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSizes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize>

trans-unit.source: For information about how you can specify a custom paper size, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om hvordan du kan angi en egendefinert størrelse, kan du se den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize"></xref> that represents the size of the paper.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSize"> </xref> som representerer størrelsen på arket.

trans-unit.source: The default is the printer's default paper size.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er skriverens standardstørrelsen på arket.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the page's paper source; for example, the printer's upper tray.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir sidens kilde; for eksempel skriverens øvre skuffen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the bounds of the printable area of the page for the printer.
trans-unit.target: Henter grensene for området som kan for skriveren.

trans-unit.source: The PrintableArea property returns the correct value, whether the page orientation is landscape or portrait.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen PrintableArea returnerer riktig verdi om retningen på er liggende eller stående.

trans-unit.source: You can use this property to print outside the margins of the page, but within the printable area.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke denne egenskapen til å skrive ut utenfor margene på siden, men innenfor området.

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.RectangleF"> </xref> som representerer lengde og bredde hundredeler tomme, for området skriveren er kan skrive ut i.
